title: Baseball Falls Twice At No. 7 Georgia Tech On Saturday To Close Series - Gardner Webb University Bulldogs
content: Baseball Falls Twice At No. 7 Georgia Tech On Saturday To Close Series  Gardner Webb University Bulldogs
description: ATLANTA, Ga. – Gardner-Webb dropped both ends of Saturday's baseball doubleheader at No. 7 Georgia Tech, falling 14-5 and 7-3 to the Yellow Jackets.
